I'm talking about a news program brought to
you by Sissy and Shaggy, your local alternative

00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:39.140
news source.

00:03:39.140 --> 00:03:40.140
&gt;&gt;Shaggy: Men from all over the country have
flooded the organization with their semen

00:03:40.140 --> 00:03:41.140
donations.

00:03:41.140 --> 00:03:42.140
&gt;&gt;Sissy: Truly an inspiring gift, Shaggy.

00:03:42.140 --> 00:03:43.140
&gt;&gt;Shaggy: People really like good news.

00:03:43.140 --> 00:03:44.140
[whistling music]

