&gt;&gt;Barbara: The hard way.

00:04:14.409 --> 00:04:15.409
&gt;&gt;Birch: You're under contract.

00:04:15.409 --> 00:04:20.820
&gt;&gt;Birch: We lose our right to pursue the American
Dreams, while suppressing your brothers.

